{"tid":1935296,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★廢老再末日！賽馬會今日(20日)宣布，場外投注處即時起暫停服務","createTime":"2020-03-20T12:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T13:12:27.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"696faf520fa0b5268a035cd788d66aa85964a64b","tid":1935296,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T12:49:57.000Z","msg":"近日本港新冠肺炎疫情轉趨嚴峻，香港賽馬會今日(20日)宣布，賽馬日開放的場外投注處及馬場，將由即時起暫停提供服務，為期兩星期，並於下月2日前再作公布。<br />\n<br />\n馬會表示，早前開放部分場外投注處及2個馬場於非賽馬日提供顧客服務，包括兌換現金券或中獎彩票，以及投注戶口存款。惟隨着大量港人於本星期初由海外返港，確診感染個案數目迅速上升，令疫情更加嚴峻，而醫學專家更警告疫情在未來期間將十分嚴峻，故此早前於非賽馬日開放的場外投注處及馬場由即時起暫停提供服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200320/bkn-20200320202049543-0320_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200320%2Fbkn-20200320202049543-0320_00822_001.html&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXN9AtAt3lYzSqFOpIRNeugk%3D&h=e0f2825b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200320/bkn-20200320202049543-0320_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"84404f71e8eba1879116a81d3b6329d5ee568e6d","tid":1935296,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T12:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5252847ea1d2f6fca980d17c08f9b3785b24b9","tid":1935296,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T12:50:32.000Z","msg":"政府：全部公共服務回復正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779449af4b7cc78d32e9546d28cc7e2d7a6d738d","tid":1935296,"uid":101945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T12:51:33.000Z","msg":"又停返 玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg